	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I have recently downloaded a copy of tUME. I tried creating a few maps with it and it worked.
<br />But there's a catch! tUME expects the tileset to be in .LBM format. I have no idea about this format. I have so far dealt with only .CHR files.
<br />
<br />Are there any tools for conversion between .CHR and .LBM?
<br />
<br />
<br />..and 1 more thing. The tUME download link on main page of NesDev is not working. 
<br />
<br />Cheers.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
