	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Unless I'm absolutely mistaken, the LBM format is simply that of old Deluxe Paint.  That format was widely in use back in the Amiga days.
<br />I don't know nawt about the mentioned CHR format or even what format(s) you convert from -&gt;CHR. IIRC, LBM and PCX are easily convertible against eachother.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


